data.description: Welcome to your new haven in Navarre! Step into this well-maintained home that's ready for you to move right in. Nestled within walking distance of West-Navarre Primary School in an esteemed ''A'' rated School District, this residence offers the perfect blend of convenience and comfort.  Ideally situated near Hurlburt Field, shopping centers, and an array of restaurants, with a short 5-mile jaunt to the stunning white sands of Navarre Beach. Home offers luxury vinyl plank flooring that spans throughout the entire home, a formal dining room and an additional room perfect for an office or den, complete with stylish barn doors for added privacy.  This retreat also boasts a host of upgrades designed to enhance your lifestyle including new LG appliances in kitchen, and stone countertops add a touch of elegance to the bathrooms. Rest easy knowing that major investments have been made, including a new roof installed in October 2019 with warranty coverage, as well as upgraded double pane windows.  Nestled at the end of a tranquil cul-de-sac, the home has a fence, newly laid sod in the front yard, and extended concrete pads in the backyard offer ample space to soak up the sunshine, while mature trees provide shade and seclusion. Plus, a new shed added in 2023 provides additional storage for all your outdoor essentials. Don't miss your chance to experience the epitome of coastal living - this home is ready and waiting for you to make unforgettable memories!
